name: Karen Gillan (Lora)
description:
💡Don't mention her name in your prompts otherwise data about her already in your model will disturb the outcomes. I actually made this lora just for avoiding bad performance of her outputs in original SD v1.5. Just type in words like "woman" (you could refer to my png info) and use this lora.

～～

Also after many tests, here it is.

In basic SD v1.5 she cannot get a good output, I tried lora and it works well.

--Trained online a week ago based on Delibrate and Ares Mix like my MEW lora, and these two seemingly get similar outcomes.

Suggested weighted 0.8~0.95. -_^

~~

Hires.fix on is suggested as always (i.e. 448*640--1.6x-->716*1024, Hires steps 18,Denoising strength 0.45, latent.)

~~

Be kind to these lovely.

Legal & Risk

It is prohibited to use this model for commercial purposes and any scenarios of illegal acts and purposes.
